## Development Environment

Local development is done on Windows (PowerShell shell). Use Windows-compatible
shell commands and paths for local tasks. Note that deployment targets Linux
(Ubuntu on AWS EC2 via the infra-repo), so the application and Docker images
must run on Linux.
